column2: "1. It seems like Aki might call me"
"2. I have a feeling Sara is going to call"
"<%me>, what's your status. How soon can you get here?"
"What's wrong. Is there something unusual about me contacting you?"
"You had a feeling I was going to call. That's generally known as deja vu."
"That aside, I've made preparations on my end and am waiting on you."
"Ah! It finally got through! <%me>, can you come to where I am?"
"You thought I was going to call right before I did?"
"Deja vu, I suppose. I wouldn't know to much about that."
"It happens to some people all of the time. It's never happened to me before though."
"But forget about that, you promised you'd come here today. You're on your way right?"
"That's why I called, to make sure you weren't slacking off on me."
